elements.text:
You play as a 
depressed bootcamp 
grad who is lost in a 
gambling habit.
After waking up inside
of a slot machine, you
find yourself stuck at 
the starting location. 
You must solve a 
puzzle to continue. An
NPC shows up and 
repeadedly offer you 
help. They express 
romantic interest in 
you and over time, 
you realize that this 
(Queen of Hearts) has
been intentionally 
making it harder for 
you to escape and 
wants to keep you 
here forever.
elements.originalText:
You play as a depressed bootcamp grad who is lost in a gambling habit.
After waking up inside of a slot machine, you find yourself stuck at the starting location. You must solve a puzzle to continue. An NPC shows up and repeadedly offer you help. They express romantic interest in you and over time, you realize that this (Queen of Hearts) has been intentionally making it harder for you to escape and wants to keep you here forever.
